name: Invoke Network Assessment Tool
description:
Using Microsoft Teams or Skype for Business Network Assessment Tool connects to nearby Microsoft node to test voice call quality (round trip time, jitter, packet loss rate, packet reorder ratio).
Results are calculated based on 90 percentile of values per metric.
Tool is applicable for quality test of Microsoft Skype for Business and Microsoft Teams.

inputs.description: Maximum random delay set to avoid overloading server hosting virtual machines. Provide number of seconds less than 600
inputs.name: MaximumDelayInSeconds

outputs.description: Round trip time latency between device and Microsoft server node
outputs.name: RTTLatency

outputs.description: Average time difference of packet arrival
outputs.name: Jitter

outputs.description: Fraction of the total transmitted packets that did not arrive at the receiver
outputs.name: PacketLossRate

outputs.description: Ratio of the total transmitted packets that did not arrive in correct order at the receiver
outputs.name: PacketReorderRatio

outputs.description: Microsoft quality test result of packet loss during test call
outputs.name: PacketLossRateTestPassed

outputs.description: Microsoft quality test result of packet round trip time during test call
outputs.name: RTTLatencyTestPassed

outputs.description: Microsoft quality test result of average jitter during test call
outputs.name: JitterTestPassed

outputs.description: Microsoft quality test result of average jitter during test call
outputs.name: PacketReorderRatioTestPassed
